agents.name: Barbara Kent, Broker/Owner
agents.slogan: Montana Roots Realty...helping you establish yours!
agents.description: Experience counts for a lot in this business.  A knowledgeable Realtor is who you need on your side.  There is plenty of paperwork, your due diligence, negotiations & more negotiations, so in order to get the most out of your sale or your purchase, finding a Realtor you like and trust is key. You'll have an advantage when you know and work with someone who has been in the business for more than 13 years, like Barb Kent, Broker/Owner of Montana Roots Realty.  Barb has been a licensed Realtor for over 13 years and has sold property all over the state of Montana.  A native Montanan and 32 year resident of Bozeman, Barb is someone you can trust as your guide throughout the whole buying or selling process.  Call Barb and put down some Montana roots today!  Why rent?  Call Barb Kent for ALL your real estate needs!

agents.name: Bronson Neff, Broker
agents.description:
Professional

I am a Realtor that strives on keeping my clients best interests at heart while delivering superb customer service. From my experiences working in the restaurant industry for most of my life, I have developed excellent interpersonal skills and know what it takes to get the job done. I specialize in single-family residential homes as well as vacant/raw land.

Personal

I was born and raised in Tucson, AZ where I earned a degree in Economics from the University of Arizona. Throughout my life I have always been very active in sports from basketball and football to snowboarding and mountain biking. I enjoy traveling and experiencing new places with friends and family.
